-- Sri Lanka to Narrow Budget Deficit Over Next Three Years, Amunugama Says
-- Anusha Ondaatjie
-- 2010-06-29T09:08:01Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-29/sri-lanka-to-narrow-budget-deficit-over-next-three-years-amunugama-says.html

          
          
             Sri Lanka will narrow its budget
deficit over the next three years, Deputy Finance Minister
Sarath Amunugama said. He was speaking in Parliament while
presenting the 2010 budget speech today.  
